item.title: [508]Changing Home
item.dc:creator: @cocoa cocoa
item.description:
@cocoa wrote:

[quote=“Barrage™, post:5, topic:236260”][quote author=cocoa link=topic=311711.msg2485249#msg2485249 date=1223773254]

[quote author=Barrage™ link=topic=311711.msg2485241#msg2485241 date=1223773052]

how do i change home to edgeville

Go to your login.java and search “teleport” Change the id’s there to the coords of edgeville.
[/quote]Rep++ and do you know how to make ::train and it goes to where the home was ‘dummys’

You would open up your commands.java which is located src>palidino76>rs2>io>packets

Then search “train” Change the coords to your dummy room. p.teleportTo(XXXX, YYYY, 0, 0, 0, 8939, 8941, 1576, 0, 1577, 0);
XXXX = X coordinate
YYYY = Y coordinate
[/quote]is it possible to add a monster to a place to stay there, like auto spawn.cfg[/quote]

i posted that on one of your posts.
